384
00:21:20,620 --> 00:21:22,500
激励 克林特
Inspiration, Clint.

385
00:21:26,410 --> 00:21:29,160
我到办公室了 下班以后咱们在安全屋见 
The office is here. Shall we meet at the safehouse after work?

386
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:34,080
如果今天的计划顺利
Uh, if all goes as planned today,

387
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:36,500
这就是咱俩最后一次见面了
this is gonna be the last time we see each other.

388
