392
00:21:48,870 --> 00:21:51,870
把你的手机号输一下 仅限紧急情况
Here, put your phone number in here. For emergencies only.

393
00:21:53,450 --> 00:21:54,790
进去吧 注意安全
Just go inside. Stay safe.

394
00:21:57,370 --> 00:21:59,450
-我拨一下 这样我就可以… -明白
-Just lettin' it ring, so I have... -Gotcha.

395
00:21:59,540 --> 00:22:00,500
有你的号码
...your number.

396
00:22:02,080 --> 00:22:04,160
仅限紧急情况 否则我就把你拉黑删除了
Emergencies only, or I'll block and delete you.

397
00:22:05,830 --> 00:22:07,040
