No, please don't.

402
00:22:15,540 --> 00:22:16,870
我有你的号码
I got your number.

403
00:22:20,660 --> 00:22:22,790
这样应该可以 我们可以先加到日程里…
That'll work. We can put it in her calendar for now and...

404
00:22:22,870 --> 00:22:24,160
毕肖普安保公司

405
