我一会就回来
Hey. Back in a sec, D.

406
00:22:30,370 --> 00:22:32,200
-你好 凯特 不行 -早上好
-Oh. Hi, Kate. Nope. Oh. -Good mornin'.

407
00:22:32,290 --> 00:22:34,450
