I'm sorry. I know. Before you say it...

408
00:22:34,540 --> 00:22:35,500
凯蒂
Katy.

409
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:37,370
早上好
Good morning.

410
00:22:37,790 --> 00:22:38,830
是凯特
Kate.

