Yeah, that's not gonna work. It's just gonna take a couple minutes...

454
00:25:21,370 --> 00:25:22,450
嘿
Uh... Hey.

455
00:25:22,540 --> 00:25:24,120
听着 我知道你是谁
Look, I know who you are,

456
00:25:24,200 --> 00:25:28,330
但是这里的大多数人都是消防员和警察
but most of those folks out there are firefighters and cops.

457
00:25:29,040 --> 00:25:32,330
如果你坏了规矩 小心吃不了兜着走
And if you break the rules, it's gonna get real messy.

458
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:40,500
什么规矩 
What are the rules?

459
00:25:42,700 --> 00:25:43,540
真人角色扮演手册

460
00:25:43,620 --> 00:25:46,410
-姓名  -不必了 谢谢
-WOName? -Uh, yeah, no, thank you.

461
00:25:46,500 --> 00:25:47,790
邮箱 
Email?

462
